org.spdx.compare

Class CompareTemplateOutputHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.spdx.compare.CompareTemplateOutputHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ILicenseTemplateOutputHandler

    public class CompareTemplateOutputHandler
extends Object
implements ILicenseTemplateOutputHandler
    Compares the output of a parsed license template to text. The method matches is called after the document is parsed to determine if the text matches.
    Author:
    Gary O'Neall
